snippet.title: Warframe | Heart of Deimos - Available now on PC, PS4 and Xbox One
snippet.description: Warframe’s third open world is available now on PC, PS4 and Xbox One! Work with the mysterious Entrati, and come face-to-face with horrifying new Infested enemies. Get full info on Heart of Deimos: http://www.warframe.com/deimos
